# Loaded by `vite build` automatically. Overrides .env for production builds.
#
# Bundle di-load lokal dari APK → tidak ada Vite proxy. VITE_API_URL harus
# absolut. CORS di WebView di-bypass oleh plugin CapacitorHttp (lihat
# capacitor.config.json) — fetch dari JS dilempar ke HTTP client native Android.
VITE_API_URL=https://s3.archives.my.id/api
